# Cursor Rules for CSHAD iSentinel News

## Project Overview
- React Native app using Expo SDK 55
- Supabase backend
- Firebase push notifications
- Google Maps integration
- Multi-language (EN, AF, ZU)

## Key Conventions
- Package name: cshad.isentinel.news
- Never use the old package: com.atg.pshad.sentinel
- All files must have a first-line comment with the project-relative path
- Full file replacements only (no partial edits unless 1-2 lines)
- Commit after every logical change
- All tools must be free and work from South Africa

## Path Aliases
- @/ = src/
- @assets/ = assets/

## Build Commands
- Type check: npx tsc --noEmit
- Run dev: npx expo start --dev-client
- Build APK: npx eas-cli build --platform android --profile preview
- Push OTA: npx eas update --branch preview --platform android --message "..."

## Environment Variables
Always use process.env.EXPO_PUBLIC_* for client-side env vars.
Document new keys in .env.example when adding.

## Common Issues
- libworklets.so duplicates: use EAS cloud build, not local
- Blank screen on launch: check fallbackToCacheTimeout is 3000
- Missing Supabase keys: check EAS environment variables are set